{
  "description": "A wide, panoramic view captures a serene seascape under a dramatic twilight sky. The foreground features the silhouetted branches of trees, contrasting sharply with the bright, expanding vista beyond. The main focal point is a long, elegant suspension bridge spanning a wide body of water. Distant hills or mountains form the backdrop, their outlines softened by the atmospheric haze. The sky is a captivating blend of colors, transitioning from deep blues and purples to fiery oranges and reds near the horizon, indicating either a sunrise or sunset. There's a subtle glow reflecting on the water's surface, adding to the tranquility of the scene. A few ships are faintly visible on the water.",
